  "title": "Logistic and catering executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Catering</strong></p><ul><li><p>Collaborate with marketing campaigns to design event catering set up</p></li><li><p>Facilitate event briefing and training with relevant operational documents</p></li><li><p>Arrange logistics for catering food deliveries, tear down, equipment transport, and event setups,</p></li><li><p>Plan and deploy of manpower and resources for catering events</p></li><li><p>Ensure proper stock control and inventory management of catering supplies, and equipment.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with customer to ensure smooth event execution and catering experience.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Logistic</strong></p><ul><li><p>Plan route and assign daily jobs to delivery drivers</p></li><li><p>Support Dispatching of orders and provide coordination with delivery drivers</p></li><li><p>supporting packing of products (when needed)</p></li></ul>",
